            <div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
                
                <p n="1-22">
                    In the fifth year of Parākrama Bahu Niśśaṅka Malla, king of Southern Laṅkā,
                    on the day of Jupiter <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>poṉṉavaṉ tiṉam</foreign><note>That is, Thursday.</note></supplied>, seven<supplied reason="subaudible">th day in</supplied> the fortnight, ... when the sun joins in the Capricorn,
                    ...
                    the vainquisher of the five<note>That is, the Pāṇḍyas?</note>,
                    ...
                    rejoiced.
                </p>
